on-s-line-appearance-package-falling-ev-sales&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/8/2/24211884/audi-q8-e-tron-s-line-appearance-package-falling-ev-sales" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/8/2/24211884/audi-q8-e-tron-s-line-appearance-package-falling-ev-sales</id><author><name>奥马尔·沙基尔</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-08-02T13:13:53-04:00</published><updated> 2024-08-02T13:13:53-04:00</updated><title>苹果再次为其一则广告道歉</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;从苹果现已撤下的“OOO（外出）”广告中截取的屏幕截图。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/MTBOHvG55RcK8D-g_TwRoHs_hO0=/121x0:2157x1357/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73498232/Apple_ooo_ad_Thailand.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;图片：Apple&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;JuebJa&quot;>;在苹果广告对泰国的过时且刻板的描述遭到强烈批评后，苹果已将其删除并发表道歉。负面关注是在&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/5/9/24153113/apple-ipad-ad-crushing-apology&quot;>;苹果为“粉碎”iPad Pro 广告道歉&lt;/ a>; 并在引起创意界的广泛批评后于 5 月从广播中删除。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;bwmey2&quot;>;“泰国人民对这则广告深感不满”，泰国议员 Sattra Sripan &lt;a href= “https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/apple-pulls-commercial-after-thai-backlash-calls-for-boycott&quot;>;彭博社报道的一份声明中说道&lt;/em>;&lt;/a>;。 “我鼓励泰国人停止使用苹果产品，转而使用其他品牌。”&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;rTLrH4&quot;>;这则名为“OOO（外出）”的 10 分钟广告是苹果公司最新的广告&lt;em>;The Underdogs&lt;/em>; 喜剧系列，描绘了一群反复出现的同事使用 Apple 产品解决工作场所中的问题的故事。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;UzRUaK&quot;>;...&lt;/p>; &lt; p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/8/2/24212005/apple-thailand-ad-pulled-underdogs-out-of-office&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt; /p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/8/2/24212005/apple-thailand-ad-pulled-underdogs-out-of-office" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/8/2/24212005/apple-thailand-ad-pulled-underdogs-out-of-office</id><author><name>杰西韦瑟贝德</name></author></entry></feed>